OL,5,G0930 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FSean and Maxine hope to give their
OL,7,     Frivals the royal treatment at The
OL,8,     FRoyal Forester in Bewdley. Some of
OL,9,     Ftheir guests are blown away by the
OL,10,     Frooms, but there's a hairy
OL,11,     Fencounter for others.
OL,12,G0955 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FMum-and-son duo Sarah and Luke
OL,14,     Fhost at Ferry Lodge in Holyhead on
OL,15,     FAnglesey. But Sean and Maxine
OL,16,     Fbegrudge paying 50p for
OL,17,     Ftoiletries, and there's confusion
OL,18,     Fover the 'Welsh' breakfast.
