OL,11,G1100 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FIt's the final day of the
OL,13,     Fcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,14,     Ffor one last time to settle some
OL,15,     Fscores and find out how much
OL,16,     Fthey've been paid. Tensions run
OL,17,     Fhigh before the winner is
OL,18,     Fannounced.
