OL,5,G1135 A Place in the Sun
OL,6,     FSharon and Nev love the beautiful
OL,7,     Fisland of Malta and want to buy a
OL,8,     Fholiday home there for all the
OL,9,     Ffamily to enjoy. With a budget of
OL,10,     F#160,000, can Ben Hillman deliver
OL,11,     Ftheir Maltese dream?
OL,12,G1235 A Place in the Sun
OL,13,     FMidwife and beautician Lisa has
OL,14,     Fbeen visiting Menorca since she
OL,15,     Fwas a child and now wants to buy a
OL,16,     Ffamily holiday home, with space to
OL,17,     Fcreate a beauty salon, in the
OL,18,     Fresort of Cala en Porter.
