OL,5,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe competition kicks off at
OL,7,     FWatergate Yard in Sleaford,
OL,8,     FLincolnshire, where hosts Ryan and
OL,9,     FHollie have a unique style and
OL,10,     F15,000 mannequins up their
