OL,5,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt Holly Hill Inn, Tom's already
OL,7,     Flet all his competitors know that
OL,8,     Fhe runs the best place in
OL,9,     FRichmond, North Yorkshire. So
OL,10,     Fwhy's he feeling so hard done by
OL,11,     Fat feedback time?
OL,12,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FBrittany hosts the week's final
OL,14,     Fvisit at Woodland Park Lakes
OL,15,     FHolidays in Windermere, where the
OL,16,     FB&Bers enjoy an arty afternoon.
OL,17,     FBut faces drop when it comes to
OL,18,     Fthe cost.
